name: XOYCoin
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Xoycoin is a utility token with the symbol: XOY. Created by Mexican developers to obtain products, services, or special benefits related to sports betting from associated XOY Capital Group companies. At the same time, there will be the opportunity to buy or sell those assets to other investors in the network, for the acquisition of products or services from companies that accept this payment method.
